1) What happens if cleaning is skipped?
If we skip cleaning, the data will have issues like missing values, duplicates, and incorrect records.
Because of this, the analysis will not be accurate and the results can be wrong.

2) Which issue impacted results most?
Missing customer_id affected the most because it is an important column for grouping and joining data.
Without it, we cannot properly identify customers, so the data becomes unreliable.

3) How would this affect business decisions?
If the data is not clean, the insights will be wrong.
This can lead to poor decisions, like targeting the wrong customers or calculating revenue incorrectly.

4) Can you define a cleaning checklist?
Yes, a simple checklist is:
Remove null values
Handle missing data
Remove duplicate records
Filter invalid values
Validate the data after cleaning
